## Requirements
* Sign up for Bluehost
* Registered Student name in BACS 350 at Shrinking World
* Registered Domain name at Shrinking-World
* Page at "bacs350/index.php"
* Stylesheet in "bacs350/index.php"
* Profile photo
* index.php includes profile.html
* Title, Icon,
* Header, Main, Footer
* reusable files for header and footer